programme.title: World Watch: Africa’s Hunter Ep3
programme.desc: Ikuti kehidupan pemangsa hebat di Zambia seperti singa, harimau bintang dan hyena, yang bersaing dalam dunia liar yang semakin mencabar. Pelbagai perubahan berlaku dari kelahiran impala serentak hingga kemunculan makhluk ganjil seperti anai-anai terbang. Alam liar Lembah ini bersedia menghadapi musim baharu. Episod kali ini mengenai pada kemuncak musim kemarau di Zambia, tiga singa betina kebanggaan Nsefu sedang bunting. Singa melindungi kelompok mereka daripada pemangsa seperti harimau bintang dan hyena.

programme.title: Bidadari: Kerana Hafsanya Setia Ep16
programme.desc: Segalanya seakan sempurna apabila Delaila dan Ali Syukri disatukan atas dasar cinta. Tapi benarlah kata orang, kahwin pada usia muda itu banyak cabarannya. Bahtera rumah tangga mereka diuji dengan kehadiran orang ketiga dan Delaila membawa diri ke New York. Dua belas tahun kemudian, pertemuan di New York telah membuka semula kisah mereka. Ali ternampak Abang Syam di jalanraya. Abang Syam meracau-racau dan tidak tentu arah. Ali membawanya berjumpa Kak Jun. Kak Jun membawa Abang Syam pulang ke kampung untuk berubat. Ali mengharap Delilah masih menerima dirinya lagi. Wairah yang baru bekerja di firma guaman Hud, telah di tegur Hud kerana tidak fokus pada kerja. Ibu Delilah, Faridah tidak suka Delilah berhubungan semula dengan Ali. Pelakon: Azrel Ismail, Mona Ellen, Octovia Menrose dan Daler Yusuf.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Aksara Kasih Ayah Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan hubungan kasih sayang seorang ayah dengan anak angkatnya. Namun apabila dugaan mendatang bagaimana pula kisah kasihnya itu, setelah isteri yang dia sayangi pula meninggal dunia. Doktor mengesyaki sel kanser wujud semula di dalam tubuh Aminah dan pemeriksaan lanjut perlu dilakukan. Aminah cuba untuk bersikap seperti biasa walaupun dia sudah mula berasa cepat letih. Pelakon: Saufi Qahhar, Wafiy Ilhan, Zamarul Hisham, Izreen Azminda dan Awang Hamyzan.

programme.title: Spektra: Derhaka Cinta Jebat Ep8
programme.desc: Semua berpunca kerana rasa dendam, salah faham dan ditambah pula dengan ego yang tinggi melangit, sanggup Jebat Zulkarnain menzalimi Aisyah Humaira isterinya sendiri. Bijaknya Jebat mengatur rancangan agar Aisyah jatuh cinta padanya hingga membawa kepada sebuah perkahwinan dengan niat ingin membalas dendam. Aisyah Humaira, suatu ketika dahulu pernah menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan adik lelaki Jebat, iaitu Tuah Iskandar. Tanpa usul periksa Jebat menjatuhkan hukuman tanpa memberi peluang kepada Aisyah untuk menjelaskan segala-galanya. Aisyah dituduh berlaku curang dengan Tuah dan menjadi penyebab musibah yang menimpa adik lelaki kesayangannya. Aisyah benar-benar kecewa. Jebat mendustai cintanya. Dia dinikahi Jebat bukan untuk disayang, dicintai sepenuh hati tapi Jebat punya agendanya sendiri. Misi Jebat hanyalah satu, melunaskan dendamnya dan membalas balik segala kesengsaraan Tuah yang kononnya dikhianati Aisyah dahulu. Pak Husin menasihatkan Aishah agar menjaga maruah suami namun Amar terus berusaha memikat Aishah. Aishah juga terus dipersalahkan atas apa yang berlaku pada Tuah. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

programme.desc: Dokumentari memaparkan isu hidupan liar dan alam semulajadi. Aishah terkilan kerana usahanya untuk berbaik dengan keluarga Jebat dipersiakan. Pelakon: Elvina Mohamad, Azlee Khairi, Ikmal Amry, Mimi Ernida, Nina Fazurina, Wilma Muhammad dan Aznah Hamid.

programme.title: Tamadun Yang Hilang Ep7

programme.title: Suamiku Mr Blind Ep9
programme.desc: Melissa pelik melihat sikap adik iparnya itu dan bertanyakan apakah yang telah terjadi. Ain terus bercerita panjang. Mengucap panjang Melissa dan terus berpesan kepada Ain supaya jangan buat lagi mengemas rumah lelaki bukan muhrim walaupun lelaki itu tua. Ain mengaku bersalah kerana terima pelawaan itu. Dalam masa yang sama, Melissa beritahu Ain nasib baiklah Aidil memang buta dan sah-sah lah bukan salah dan niatnya untuk terpeluk Ain. Ain beritahu dia rasa bersalah pada Ryan. Ketika berjumpa Ryan, Ain memberitahu jika mereka berkahwin Ain akan berhenti kerja kerana mahu jaga hubungan suami isteri namun Ryan beritahu dia langsung tidak kisah dan cemburu. Ain rasa amat lega. Ketika sedang melakukan spot check dan ingin masak di rumah Aidil, Adila amat terkejut apabila ada baju perempuan di rumah Aidil di atas katilnya pula tu. Adila menyuruh Aidil berterus-terang dan Aidil dengan jujur memberitahu yang Ain ada datang ke rumahnya bagi membantu dia mengemas rumah tetapi tidak tahu kenapa baju Ain tertinggal. Aidil mula berfikir yang bukan-bukan.

Puan Ainon dan Encik Ismail memang teruja menerima bakal menantu cuma Puan Ainon tertanya-tanya bagaimana orangnya Entah kenapa Ain menunggu panggilan telefon daripada Aidil. Rindu pula suara bosnya itu. Melissa mengusik, rindu bos takpa, jangan rindu perkara lain tentang bos. Kembali ke Kuala Lumpur, Ryan memperkenalkan adik angkatnya iaitu Wani kepada Ain. Kononnya Wani akan membantu Ain menguruskan perkahwinan mereka. Ain hanya diam tetapi timbul juga rasa cemburu melihat kemesraan adik dan abang angkat itu. Sampailah satu hari ketika Puan Maimon sengaja ingin mengejutkan Ryan untuk membantu menguruskan perkahwinannya, dia sorok-sorok ke rumah sewa Ryan dan alangkah terkejutnya nampak Ryan bersama dengan Wani.

programme.title: 3AM EP1 Ep1
programme.desc: Pesta Hantu Lapar sudah hampir. Seorang pekerja baru di telah menyinggung perasaan hantu di bangunan pejabatnya kerana dia tidak hormat kepada roh pada hari pertamanya bekerja. Semasa menjalani syif malam, lelaki itu dan rakan sekerjanya yang bekerja lebih masa mengalami pertemuan menyeramkan yang membuatkan mereka merenung tingkah laku dan kepercayaan mereka.

programme.title: Taxi 3
programme.desc: Sekumpulan pencuri yang menggelarkan diri mereka sebagai Geng Santa Claus sedang menimbulkan kekacauan, dan polis tidak dapat mengejarnya. Kapten polis Gilbert terganggu oleh seorang wartawan Cina yang menulis cerita tentang skuadnya, isteri detektif Emilien baru sahaja mengumumkan bahawa dia hamil, dan pemandu teksi Daniel sedang mengalami krisis hubungan. Selepas rentetan kesilapan di mana pencuri mengakali polis berkali-kali dengan wartawan di sana untuk merakam semuanya, Daniel dan teksi supernya masuk.

programme.title: Black Demon
programme.desc: Percutian keluarga berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila mereka berdepan dengan seekor jerung megalodon ganas. Terdampar dan diserang tanpa henti, Paul dan keluarganya mesti mencari jalan untuk kembali ke pantai dengan selamat sebelum jerung itu menyerang lagi.

programme.title: Taxi 4
programme.desc: Tidak bernasib baik, kikir, tetapi menawan, detektif PD Marseille milien Coutant-Kerbalec mesti membantu komisioner Gibert yang lebih teruk daripada Clouseau menjaga penjenayah Belgium yang terkenal sebagai bahaya sama seperti - dan ditawan seperti Hannibal Lector. Kawan sejuk milien, pemandu teksi Daniel Morales, pada mulanya hanya bersetuju untuk menjaga anak-anak lelaki kawan mereka, kerana isteri milien, Petra, sedang menjalankan misi rahsia. Tetapi tidak lama kemudian, penjenayah Belgium itu melarikan diri, dan semasa mengejarnya, rakan-rakan itu tersandung pada satu perampokan bank dan sebuah vila megah milik raja dadah, di mana babak akhir yang hebat berlaku.

programme.desc: Kisah ini mengisahkan tentang Kamasani, seorang tokoh perniagaan yang menghidap kanser tahap akhir, yang mencari Mahabub, seorang pertapa misteri yang dikhabarkan memiliki penawar. programme.title: Wangi
programme.desc: Nor dan suaminya, Khuzairi tinggal di sebuah banglo bersama dua anak mereka. Selepas melahirkan anak kedua, Nor pulang ke rumah dan ibunya datang untuk menjaganya. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

programme.title: Jaket Biru
programme.desc: Untuk menumpaskan sebuah kumpulan penyeludupan anak gadis ke luar negara, pihak polis telah menubuhkan sebuah pasukan rahsia yang bernama Jaket Biru. Pasukan yang diketuai oleh Azizan itu ditugaskan untuk melakukan intipan dengan menyertai aktiviti haram tersebut.

programme.title: Paloh
programme.desc: Berlatar belakangkan tahun 1944, ketika konflik antara komunis dan tentera Jepun, filem ini mengisahkan Ahmad, yang bekerja dengan tentera Jepun, telah jatuh cinta dengan seorang gadis Cina bernama Siew Lan.

programme.title: Gerak Khas The Movie 3
programme.desc: Unit Gerak Khas cuba menyelesaikan kes pembunuhan Suzana di sebuah pangsapuri mewah yang dipercayai mempunyai kaitan dengan Ramon yang merupakan adik kepada Frankie, penjenayah yang ditumpaskan oleh Unit Gerak Khas dalam satu operasi menentang kumpulan militan dan sindiket pengedaran dadah 2 tahun yang lalu.

programme.title: Konstabel Mamat
programme.desc: Akibat kelalaian dalam operasi menangkap ketua gengster iaitu Mail Musang yang merupakan bapa ayam sindiket pelacuran di Kuala Lumpur, Mamat digantung tugas selama tiga bulan. Meskipun digantung, Mamat tetap rajin dan menjalankan tugas menangkap penjenayah. Mamat yang jatuh cinta dengan kekasih gelap kepada Mail Musang telah diketahui olehnya. Kejadian ini telah membawa kepada penangkapan Mail dan Mamat tidak lagi digantung tugas.

programme.title: Embun
programme.desc: Berlatarkan zaman penjajahan Jepun di Tanah Melayu, filem ini mengisahkan Embun, seorang wanita yang sentiasa bersemangat dan cekal dalam perjuangan menentang pencerobohan Jepun walaupun menempuh pelbagai dugaan dan cabaran.

programme.title: Prebet Lapok
programme.desc: Kisah Badul Lapok , seorang pemuda kampung nakal yang menganggur namun berubah setelah menjadi seorang anggota tentera dan menjadi wira dalam mempertahankan kedaulatan negara.

programme.title: Raja Laut
programme.desc: Para pelaut sering terancam dengan kegiatan seorang lanun bernama Raja Laut yang sering melakukan keganasan. Oleh kerana Raja Laut sangat licik dalam kegiatan haramnya, pihak berkuasa mengalami kesukaran untuk memberkasnya. Dalam masa yang sama, Raja Laut telah menjalinkan hubungan dengan adik seorang pegawai tentera laut yang menyukarkan lagi pihak berkuasa untuk menangkapnya.

programme.title: Gerak Khas The Movie
programme.desc: Unit Gerak Khas ditugaskan untuk menghapuskan sindiket pengedaran VCD haram dan pil khayal yang didalangi dua kumpulan. Dalam masa yang sama Inspektor Shafikah telah ditugaskan untuk membantu siasatan tersebut. Kehadiran Inspektor Shafikah disenangi oleh semua anggota unit terutamanya Inspektor Mazlan. Hal ini menimbulkan rasa cemburu Inspektor Aleza namun atas misi menghancurkan dua kumpulan penjenayah itu, dia mengenepikan soal peribadi.

programme.title: Wira Angkasa
programme.desc: Filem yang mengisahkan Iskandar Muhammad (Sabree Fadzil) yang merupakan anak seorang pesawah bercita-cita tinggi untuk menjadi seorang juruterbang selepas tamat pengajian dan telah menyertai Tentera Udara Di Raja Malaysia (TUDM) sehingga menjadi salah seorang pegawai.

programme.title: Gerak Khas The Movie 2
programme.desc: Unit Gerak Khas ditugaskan untuk menyiasat satu sindiket penyeludupan dadah terbesar di Malaysia yang didalangi oleh Raziman. Dua orang pegawai polis, Inspektor Zamri dan Inspektor Julia telah menyertai unit tersebut untuk membantu siasatan. Kehadiran Inspektor Zamri tidak disenangi oleh Inspektor Mazlan kerana dia mengesyaki Inspektor Zamri telah bekerjasama dengan Raziman.

programme.desc: Adnan, seorang penunggang motosikal jalanan yatim piatu yang dijaga oleh ibu saudaranya. Sebaliknya, Nadia dilahirkan dalam keluarga kaya dan kini memiliki pekerjaan yang stabil. Kedua-dua insan yang berbeza ini bertemu secara kebetulan dan akhirnya menjalin hubungan. Kini, dalam "Adnan Sempit 2", Shaheizy Sam kembali memegang watak sebagai Adnan, mengisahkan cabaran dan dugaan dalam kehidupannya serta hubungannya dengan Nadia.

programme.title: Sejoli
programme.desc: Jo (Bront Palarae) dan Gina (Maya Karin) sedang menyembuhkan hati yang terluka di Phuket apabila takdir mempertemukan mereka. Pada mulanya mereka saling membenci, tetapi apabila mereka mendapat tahu bahawa bekas kekasih masing-masing, Hardy (Remy Ishak) dan Nita (Izara Aishah), akan berkahwin, mereka merancang untuk menggagalkan majlis perkahwinan tersebut.

programme.title: Misteri Mary Kuale
programme.desc: Aileena sebenarnya anak angkat kepada Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar. Mereka menemui Aileena di dalam sebuah kotak yang ditinggalkan di tepi tong sampah. Pada masa tersebut, Puan Katrina dan Tuan Haidar baru dua tahun berkahwin. Melihat sahaja bayi perempuan yang comel itu, Puan Katrina langsung jatuh kasih dan meminta izin kepada suaminya untuk menjaga bayi itu. Aileena sentiasa didatangi mimpi mengenai seorang wanita gila berketurunan cina . Dalam mimpinya itu Aileena dipanggil anak dan dia sentiasa melarikan diri daripada wanita itu. adakah maksud tersirat disebalik mimpi itu?

programme.title: Gerabak Cinta
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luna, usahawan berjaya yang ditipu tunangnya, Razi. Dia kecewa apabila perniagaan yang mereka usahakan rugi kerana Razi terbabit dengan skandal wang serta mempunyai perempuan simpanan. Sementara itu, Gie pula baru saja dibuang kerja. Walaupun masih mencari kerja, dia sangat tenang dan tetap ceria. Gie reda dengan situasi menimpanya.

programme.title: Jodoh Tak Salah Alamat
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Luqman pernah mengenali seorang gadis bernama Diana ketika Diana melanggar keretanya dahulu. Diana berpenampilan seksi dan mengamalkan cara hidup barat membuatkan Luqman bersangka buruk terhadap Diana. Satu hari, Luqman ke masjid dan terserempak dengan seorang gadis cantik iaitu Adawiyah. Tanpa mengetahui, Adawiyah dan Diana adalah orang yang sama. Diana pernah terlibat dengan kemalangan dan sejak itu hidupnya berubah sepenuhnya.

programme.title: Taikun
programme.desc: Mengisahkan dua lelaki bernama Tai dan Kun, sahabat baik yang hanya meminati pergaduhan dan mencuri. Apabila tabiat buruk mereka menyebabkan mereka bertembung dan memukul teruk ahli geng Pink dan Purple, Tai dan Kun kemudian direkrut oleh ketua geng yang kagum dengan kemahiran mereka.

programme.title: Abang Long Fadil
programme.desc: Abang Long Fadil, seorang lelaki yang sentiasa berangan bahawa kehidupannya seperti seorang gangster. Tetapi apabila sahabat baiknya, Malik dimasukkan ke penjara, lebih banyak kekacauan berlaku dan angan-angannya mungkin tidak jauh berbeza daripada realiti.

programme.title: Ruang Temu S1 Ep51
programme.desc: Program temu bual bersama Tony Eusoff yang mengupas pengalaman peribadi beliau berkaitan pengalaman beliau di dalam industri seni

programme.title: Lebuhraya Ke Neraka
programme.desc: Lebuhraya Ke Neraka mengisahkan sekumpulan penunggang motosikal yang kasar berhenti di tepi jalan, dan tidak lama kemudian, kesemua merekakecuali Bobjatuh sakit secara misteri.

programme.title: Sampai 7 Keturunan
programme.desc: Dalam satu peraduan cabutan bertuah, Aidil telah terpilih untuk memenangi percutian lima hari empat malam di sebuah hotel lima bintang serta wang tunai sebanyak lima ribu ringgit. Namun begitu, disebabkan isterinya Syikin yang sedang hamil, Aidil memutuskan untuk tidak mengambil percutian tersebut. Walaupun begitu, Aidil berasa sayang untuk melepaskan hadiah itu begitu sahaja. Dia memberikan wang tunai dan tiket tersebut kepada Pak Karim, yang pada mulanya keberatan untuk menerimanya kerana bimbang meninggalkan ayam kesayangannya. Setelah dipujuk berkali-kali, Pak Karim akhirnya bersetuju walaupun masih risaukan ayamnya.

programme.title: Reaksiar S1 Ep7
programme.desc: Program yang memaparkan perkongsian pengalaman dan reaksi artis-artis jemputan setelah melihat kembali klip-klip lakonan mereka.

programme.title: Cincin Pusaka
programme.desc: Alina dan Sofian adalah dua beradik yang saling cemburu, berlumba mengalahkan satu sama lain sejak kecil. Setelah kematian nenek, mereka berebut untuk memiliki cincin pusaka nenek yang kononnya mempunyai magis tertentu. Tetapi pelbagai halangan terjadi untuk mereka mewarisinya. Mampukah mereka menghadapi segala rintangan demi sebentuk cincin pusaka?

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal.

programme.title: Nada Siar S1 Ep51
programme.desc: Sebuah program yang menyajikan kepada anda klip-klip video soundtrack yang terkandung dalam filem-filem klasik tempatan.

programme.title: Aji Noh Motor
programme.desc: Aji ialah seorang abang yang sangat mengambil berat dan sanggup melakukan apa sahaja untuk adiknya, Noh. Noh, seorang yang berpegang kepada ajaran Islam, berasa tidak senang dengan tabiat Aji yang suka berlumba haram. Noh dilahirkan buta dan menjalani kehidupannya dengan melakukan perkara-perkara yang berfaedah, manakala abangnya pula gemar menyertai perlumbaan haram dan melepak bersama rakan-rakannya. Walaupun Aji mempunyai perangai yang tidak baik, dia sangat menyayangi Noh. Dia sanggup memenuhi permintaan Noh walaupun permintaan itu mustahil untuk dicapai. Semuanya bermula pada hari lahir Noh apabila dia menyatakan hasrat untuk menunaikan haji. Aji yang tidak mampu untuk menunaikan permintaan tersebut telah berusaha mengumpul wang demi merealisasikan impian adiknya. Walaupun terpaksa melakukan perkara yang haram dan bertentangan dengan agama.

programme.title: Tukul Arwana One Man Show Ep6
programme.desc: Sebuah program bual bicara yang dihoskan Tukul Arwana di Indosiar menyajikan hiburan terbaru yang akan menemani penonton semasa pandemik COVID-19 bersama bintang jemputan, tokoh masyarakat dan mereka yang tular di media sosial.

programme.title: Indahnya Kebersamaan Ep41
programme.desc: Indahnya Kebersamaan ialah sebuah program tausiah yang dikendalikan oleh Mellya Baskarani bersama Prof. Dr. K.H. Nasaruddin Umar, M.A. Program ini memberi fokus kepada pelbagai permasalahan yang sering dialami oleh masyarakat, termasuk isu dalam kehidupan berumah tangga.

programme.title: Biarin Gembul Yang Penting Manisnya Pas
programme.desc: Nita sering dibuli oleh rakan-rakan sekampusnya, terutama sekali Sarah, kerana fizikalnya yang gemuk. Namun begitu, seorang Pembantu Pensyarah bernama Arya sentiasa membela dan melindungi Nita. Arya sering teringat akan kenangan lama bersama seseorang yang pernah sangat bermakna dalam hidupnya, dan sejak bertemu Nita, dia berusaha untuk mencarinya.

programme.title: Superstar Junior S1 Ep7
programme.desc: Superstar Junior Indonesia ialah pertandingan bakat kanak-kanak yang disiarkan di Mentari TV. Rancangan ini menampilkan peserta cilik dari seluruh negara yang menunjukkan bakat dalam nyanyian, tarian dan lakonan untuk memikat hati juri dan penonton.

programme.title: Doyan Makan Ep9
programme.desc: Doyan Makan menjemput penonton untuk mengikuti perjalanan dan pengalaman kulinari untuk makanan popular di kawasan tersebut, serta akan meninjau informasi tentang tempat, harga dan proses penghasilan makanan yang mereka nikmati.

programme.title: My Heart Ep24
programme.desc: Raisa yang patah hati selepas tunangnya, Rio, hilang tiba-tiba, pergi ke Jakarta untuk mencari jawapan. Di sana, dia bertemu Mike, seorang pelakon drama popular yang sebenarnya berperwatakan sensitif dan bermasalah, berbeza dengan wataknya di kaca TV. Perkenalan mereka secara kebetulan menjadi semakin rapat apabila mereka mula mengenali diri sebenar masing-masing. Namun, cinta mereka diuji apabila terbongkar bahawa ibu Mike, Rika, adalah isteri kedua kepada ayah Raisa, menyebabkan perebutan harta antara keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Lensa Lokal Medan Ep2
programme.desc: Lensa Lokal Medan merupakan sebuah dokumentari yang menyelami kehidupan masyarakat tempatan serta keunikan budaya di Medan.

programme.desc: Aji menjual ubat setiap hari dengan menaiki basikal. Ketika bertemu pelanggan, mereka berkata, ubat yang Aji jual lebih mahal berbanding yang dijual oleh Jupri, juga seorang pengedar ubat-ubatan. Dia juga membuka kedai ubatnya. Sangkaan Aji berakhir apabila Jupri bertemu dengan pembekal ubat tiruan.

programme.desc: Ungkap Hikmah Di Balik Dosa adalah sebuah rancangan yang menilai kejadian atau peristiwa dari perspektif Islam, mengungkap hikmah di sebalik dosa.

programme.desc: Dafri baru saja kembali ke Indonesia untuk bertemu dengan Alina dan bertunang. programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan Ep5159
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: The Last Dance
programme.desc: Amid the recession caused by the pandemic, debt-ridden wedding planner, Sheng, finds a lifeline as he transitions into a funeral planner. His unconventional approach leads to unexpected success, and his attitude toward his career and life is transformed after being inspired by the respected Master Wen.

programme.title: Quan Dao: The Journey of a Boxer
programme.desc: Ah Niu learns boxing from Uncle Xing, the boss of a boxing studio, since young and uses his skills to help the weak fight villains. When Xings son attempts drug trafficking to save his fathers studio but fails and is brutally beaten up, Ah Niu accepts a death combat challenge so as to help him take revenge.

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Life Must Go On
programme.desc: When the midnight gymnasium programme for wayward teenage girls is at funding risk, social worker Yanki puts together a dodgeball team to compete in a match and save it. With an ex-star athlete John as the coach, the girls realize they must face their problems and overcome their challenges instead of dodging them. Can they finally win the match?

programme.title: Bursting Point
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Bang sends Officer Ming undercover to a drug cartel to displace drug lord Yang. A failed raid triggers Yang's rage for revenge. Meanwhile, drug maker Ying Xiu is forced to cooperate with the police and sets a trap for Yang. The battle between the police and the drug cartel has just begun!

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Chilli Laugh Story
programme.desc: Coba is forced to work at home during COVID-19 and fights with his family every day. He decides to turn his mothers chilli sauce into a trendy commodity to keep his family occupied. With his mother, father and aunt making the chilli sauce together, the family sells it online and the business grows beyond their imagination.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: Once in a Blue Moon
programme.desc: Mei Zhens family appears to get along but harbours deep secrets. Mei Zhen is trapped in a dead-end job with a toxic boss, her brother hides his separation and their mother grapples with lingering guilt over her husbands departure years ago. As Mid-Autumn Festival approaches, can the family heal their wounds and find a way back to each other?

programme.title: The Fate of Reunion
programme.desc: Thousands of years ago, Green Snake gained enlightenment under the guidance of Dao Qing and gradually falls for him. However, her devotion to Dao Qing caused him to reincarnate and go through the pains of death. Since then, she sets out to search for the many reincarnations of Dao Qing over hundreds of years to help him reverse the situation

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say yes?

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Man on the Edge
programme.desc: On the eve of the 1997 handover, violence is rampant with triad forces causing chaos in Hong Kong. The triad gang leader assigns his right-hand man Ah Lok to take charge of the drug trafficking business. However, Ah Lok turns out to be an undercover police officer who unveils a shocking political conspiracy during the investigation.

programme.title: Love at First Lie
programme.desc: An ordinary, cheerful and kind-hearted girl Bao, meets a troubled rich guy Edward by chance one summer. To ruin his fathers remarriage plans, Edward hires Bao and her friend to sabotage the wedding and that is how Bao and Edward meet and fall in love. All seems well for the sweet couple until their love quickly takes an unexpected turn

programme.title: Ah Boys to Men
programme.desc: Ken is a rich and spoiled young man reluctant to be enlisted into National Service but must do so by law. He has to endure harsh training but it is made more bearable when he befriends three other recruits. When his girlfriend breaks up with him, Ken tries all ways to escape from camp so as to chase her back, but this leads to dire consequences

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar 2
programme.desc: The movie tells the story of Tang Bo Hu and his three buddies before they become the four great talents in Jiangnan. Tang Bo Hu encounters a beautiful girl when studying in a monastery and they quickly fall in love, but her hidden identity is accidentally unveiled when Tang and friends uncover a conspiracy at the monastery.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: An Abandoned Team
programme.desc: Uncle Jia is bad-tempered and lives alone. His forced retirement, failed marriage and strained relationship with his daughter have left him in despair, prompting him to consider ending his life. Fortunately, he is rescued by a stray dog and an animal welfare volunteer, allowing him to rediscover his purpose in life.

programme.title: Mr & Mrs Incredible
programme.desc: Middle-aged and retired superhero couple, Huan (Gazer Man) and Red (Aroma Woman), settles into a contented life in a remote village. They find it hard to contain their powers though, and are bored by the uneventful life. When they hear a world martial arts contest is to be held in their village, both are itching to make their long-awaited comeback!

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of The Way We Dance features the plight of Hong Kongs grassroots performing artists as they fight against the governments plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: I Did It My Way
programme.desc: As the secretive, complex world of online drug trafficking increasingly targets Hong Kong, the police launches a risky and top-secret sting operation to bring down one of the most notorious drug lords in Asia.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: My Indian Boyfriend
programme.desc: This is a love story between a Hong Kong girl and an Indian boy and is the first Bollywood movie to be made in Hong Kong. It encapsulates the conflicts caused by discrimination as well as differences in social-cultural background, lifestyle and family values between the races. The movie also combines tears, joy and laughter with song and dance.

programme.title: Septet: The Story of Hong Kong
programme.desc: Seven of Hong Kong's most revered directors, all with distinctly unique styles, come together for the first time to compose a symphony of stories for their city from the 50s to the future.

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 1
programme.desc: Wu Dang Sects Zhang Chui Shans son, Zhang Wu Ji, finds himself accidentally embroiled in the fight for the Dragon Sabre. When he unwittingly learns the powerful martial arts skills from the Jiuyin scriptures, Wu Ji proceeds to help the Six Major sects fight against the corrupt government.

programme.title: Adventure of the King
programme.desc: The Ming Emperor Zhengde flees the palace to see the world after his mother orders him to marry an ugly princess. He disguises as a commoner and escapes with his advisors, but a gambling mishap causes them to part ways and Zhengde lost all his money. Phoenix, the owner of Lung Fung Inn, takes him in out of pity, and thus begins his new adventure...

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Raging Fire
programme.desc: As the police sets to arrest a drug lord, a team of masked thugs steals the drugs and murders the cops. Inspector Bong is devastated to see the aftermath of the carnage and soon discovers that the killers are led by Ngo, a former fellow cop who was forced into a life of crime by him. As the two men meet again, it is time to settle the score

programme.title: The Trail of the Broken Blade
programme.desc: Chivalrous swordsman Fung goes in search of another swordsman on the run, Li Yue, in order to reunite him with his love. Though both men meet and end up being close friends, Li Yue did not reveal his true identity until Fungs life is endangered by a gang looking for revenge...

programme.title: The Adventures of Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung travels incognito to Jiangnan to review his peoples livelihood but soon discovers that corrupt officials are oppressing his people. The emperor meets an upright young man and they join hands to teach the corrupt officials a lesson. The young man was appointed as his bodyguard thereafter.

programme.title: The Web of Death
programme.desc: To rule the martial arts world, the Head of the Snake Sect seeks to possess a deadly plant called Five Poison Web, spreading rumours on its whereabouts. Brothers Xiong and Kit are sent to investigate. Xiong falls in love with Su who has a clue of where the plant is, but she accidentally hurts Kit when seeking the plant, devastating Xiong.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Long Chase
programme.desc: Governor Yan is killed and his guard Fan identifies Kou as the assassin by his signature weapon, a dart. Kou is listed as a wanted man when he enters the city, but managed to escape arrest with the help of the innkeepers daughter. At the same time, Fan is attacked by a bandit who pretends to be Kou. What are the secret plots behind these attacks?

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Crazy Nuts Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: A roadside bandit and a traveling gambler team up to make money from gambling. In a successful attempt to steal a huge amount of money from a warlords home, they encounter revolutionists who seek their help to fund the reform campaign. Will the two help the revolutionists cause with the stolen money?

programme.title: The Enchanting Ghost
programme.desc: It is love beyond the grave, as a young scholar and his beautiful lover are torn apart forever by his dastardly uncle and his friend, who drive the girl to commit suicide... but with death comes revenge for the enchanting ghost. A spooky yet heart-wrenching tale...

programme.title: My Young Auntie
programme.desc: An elderly landowner marries young Dai Nan to keep his inheritance away from his unscrupulous nephew before he dies. When Dai Nan brings along the deed to meet his other nephew, a series of amusing incidents happen with this young auntie, the nephew and his son. Kara Hui won Best Actress in the first Hong Kong Film Awards for her role as Dai Nan.

programme.title: Call of the Sea
programme.desc: A young fisherman, Chin Hu is in love with his childhood friend Hsiao Yu. However, the only son of a town bully lusts after Hsiao Yus beauty and tries all possible ways to approach her. Chin Hu protects another woman from the bully one day, leading Hsiao Yu to misunderstand him and suspect that they are having an affair...

programme.title: A Friend from Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness in life. One day, he meets and befriends a kind-hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: Lovers Blades
programme.desc: The Lovers Blades, a pair of invincible weapons, are to be delivered to the Qing Emperor. However, they accidentally fell into the hands of Xiao Zhong Hui and Yuan Guan Nan, so Imperial Chief Zhuo Tian Xiong hunts them down for the blades. As the battle begins, the secret of the blades are also revealed.

programme.title: To Kill a Mastermind
programme.desc: A ruthless crime syndicate, Qi Sha clan, which is controlled by seven chiefs is terrorizing China. The Imperial Court orders Minister Yang to bring them down by sending undercovers to the clan and disintegrating them from the inside. As more internal conflicts occur, will the masterminds of the clan find out who are the spys?

programme.title: Hong Kong Rhapsody
programme.desc: Hong Kong rhapsody is a musical extravaganza full of song and dance! Peter Chen-Ho stars as a playboy magician who changes his ways after he becomes the guardian of a young singer (Li Ching), the daughter of a deceased magician friend.

programme.title: The Assassin
programme.desc: Notorious assassin Nieh Cheng has retired into hiding. However, when Premier Yen's family is massacred, he seeks out the reclusive swordsman and coaxes him into a final revenge mission in this epic story set in the Six Kingdom era.

programme.title: Twinkle Twinkle Little Star
programme.desc: A beautiful but ignorant woman is abducted by aliens but nobody believes her close encounter. While planning a suicide to prove herself, she meets a failed detective who is also planning his suicide. They change their minds about dying after finding each other and start to encounter bizarre adventures, before falling in love with each other.

programme.title: Mad Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Master Chen was an esteemed Monkey Kung Fu master, until he is framed and crippled by a ruthless villain and ends up becoming a wandering artiste. When Chen meets a young man, Little Monkey, on the streets, he decides to teach him all his monkey kung fu moves. Both men eventually team up to avenge Chens past insult.

programme.title: Les Belles
programme.desc: Acknowledged as one of the greatest Hong Kong musicals, this lavish movie starring Linda Lin, who won Best Actress for her performance, infuses its wispy plot with style and wit, and the results are pure pleasure.

programme.title: Full Moon Scimitar
programme.desc: Swordsman Ding fought against many swordsmen and won, so he took his first defeat badly and wanted to commit suicide. It is then that he meets the granddaughter of a mystic Sect leader and falls in love. When they want to get married, the Sect leader presents Ding with the Full Moon Scimitar, on the condition that he will never leave the sect.

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Huis husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and causes her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.title: Mercenaries From Hong Kong
programme.desc: Filmmaker Wong Jing produced Mercenaries From Hong Kong, his very first modern-day adventure drama. In the dramatic plot he wrote, he sends superstars Ti Lung, Chen Hui-min, Wang Lung-wei, Lo Lieh and Wang Yu on a deadly mission. The film's action sequences are all closely guided by three great kung fu choreographers, led by Tang Chia!

programme.title: Mist Over Dream Lake
programme.desc: A young girl Chen is sent away by her parents who are going through divorce, to stay with the Changs. On the Changs farm, she meets their two sons, the youngest daughter and a young artist, and spends a summer with them that she will never forget.

programme.title: To Kill a Jaguar
programme.desc: Set in 1920s Shanghai, a village girl journeys to the big city in search of her father and meets her childhood friend Jaguar, who works for the mob boss Kam. In a world controlled by the mobs, it is a test of survival for all as Jaguar allies himself with ace gunman Ko Tang, to take over Kams empire.

programme.title: The Brave Archer 3
programme.desc: Guo Jing and Huang Rong go to Iron Palm Peak to search for the Book of Wumu. The chief of Iron Palm discovers their visit, and seriously injures Huang. It seems only the Southern Emperor Duan can heal her, but will Huang be healed in time?

programme.title: Shaolin Abbot
programme.desc: Monk Chi San is sent by his Shaolin Master to learn a special kung fu skill from a Wu Dang priest. He gets embroiled in a fight between the Qing and Ming camps along the way, and has to gather disciples to rebuild the burnt Shaolin temple at the same time.

programme.title: The Mad Monk Strikes Again
programme.desc: The Mad Monk is up against the equally legendary scholar-turned-genie, Lu Tung Pin. The duo create havoc as they vie with each other, be it in mirth, magic, women or weapons!

programme.title: Crippled Avengers
programme.desc: Chu Twin becomes crazy after his sons arms were chopped off. For no reason, he harms four people causing them various disabilities. The four disabled form a band to learn Kung Fu from a master, in order to take revenge on Chu Twin.

programme.title: Hex after Hex
programme.desc: Hell may have no fury like a woman scorned, but hell literally, really has no wrath like a lusting ghost scorned! Cult classic director Kuei Chih-hung shoots the works with this amazing horror romance starring muscular "Venom" Lo Meng.

programme.title: King Gambler
programme.desc: This film was actually a lively forerunner to the gambling film craze, which eventually swept Asian cinema. Here, it's cardsharp versus cardsharp with a lot more kung-fu action, in a battle of wits and fists to become the king of the casino. The double stings and triple crosses raise in complexity and imagination until what started as an unusual box office risk became a top ten hit of 1976.

programme.title: The Younger Generation
programme.desc: A tragic tale about a young girl who gets married and has five kids. When she and her husband die, leaving all five kids behind to fend for themselves, the eldest child is forced to be sold into prostitution to feed the other four.

programme.title: Monkey Kung Fu
programme.desc: Wei Chun is a cocky young man sentenced to jail for killing a man in a fight. One day, Wei Chun picks a fight with a seemingly defenseless old man who completely thrashes him! The old man turns out to be the master of monkey style kung fu and as they become friends, he gives Wei Chun half of a medallion that would direct him to hidden secrets.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang plays the all-new one-armed hero - a swordsman who chops off his right arm rather than live with dishonour. When the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by the evil gang, it is time to battle.

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: Australia's Hidden Islands S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Fraser Island - Just to the south of the Great Barrier Reef and the Tropic of Capricorn, Fraser Island lies like a sprawling lizard. Some 120 kilometers long and up to 25 kilometers wide, Fraser Island is now the largest sand island on Earth. Somehow on this nutrient-poor bed of sand life has thrived. Dingoes patrol its forests in search of wallabies while white-bellied sea eagles scour the beaches from above. From the lakes to the forests and its crystal clear streams - Fraser Island is a unique mosaic of unlikely habitats that have earned it World Heritage Status.

programme.title: Messy goes to OKIDO S1 Ep33
programme.desc: Fossil Puzzle - In the real world, Messy is bored of his dino-jigsaw. In OKIDO, his friends help him piece together a real prehistoric puzzle!

programme.title: Bluey S3 Ep17
programme.desc: Pavlova - Mum won't let Bingo have Pavlova, so the kids find a way by playing a cheeky game of Caf in the kitchen. But Dad the chef sets up a competing shop that only serves edamame beans.

programme.title: Bluey S3 Ep16
programme.desc: Phones - Bluey and Bingo want to play restaurants with Grandad, but it's a little different than he's used to... he's going to need an app to order the food!

programme.title: Hey Duggee S5 Ep6
programme.desc: The Why Badge - Why do my feet hurt?', Tag asks Duggee. While Duggee has a think, he tells them 'why' is a great question, and the Squirrels are quick to follow up.

programme.title: Hey Duggee S5 Ep5
programme.desc: The Mime Badge - Duggee is encouraging the Squirrels to come outside by gesturing through the window. They don't understand what he's doing and think it's funny. When he comes inside, he explains that he was miming.

programme.title: Hey Duggee's Squirrel Club S1 Ep2
programme.desc: Hey Quacky! - Worm and Ladybird wonder what's going on at Squirrel Club. There's a gorilla playing drums, some helpful ducks, a hot frog, four goats and a hospital run by chicken doctors.

programme.title: Hey Duggee's Squirrel Club S1 Ep3
programme.desc: Frog Song - It's fun on the counting train until Naughty Monkey starts to drive! Ethel makes a shape, Frog drops beats with a ribbit song, and Enid turns into anime to chase after a mouse.

programme.title: Go Jetters S2 Ep32
programme.desc: Everglades National Park, Florida - The Go Jetters save the Florida Everglades when hungry alligators chase Glitch's picnic.

programme.title: Bluey S1 Ep28
programme.desc: Grannies - A game of 'grannies' is fun, until Bluey and Bingo can't agree on one simple question: Can Grannies dance? Now they need to video call Nana to get the answer.

programme.title: Bluey S1 Ep27
programme.desc: Pirates - It's an adventure on the high seas as Bluey, Bingo and Missy play Pirates on the hammock swing, but they'll need to find their courage to withstand storms and whale attacks.

programme.title: Andy's Baby Animal Missions S1 Ep10
programme.desc: Andy and the Baby Kangaroos - In this episode Andy, Jen and Scout head to Australia on a baby animal mission to solve the mystery of why a group of kangaroos, and their joeys, are living on a beach. Along the way, Andy is chased by a pack of dingoes and hops to safety with the baby kangaroos.

programme.title: Dog Squad S2 Ep16
programme.desc: Mission: Pop-Pop Lost - Search and rescue dog Dan and his owner Jamie set off on an urban search, looking for Pop-Pop who has got lost while exploring near his care home.

programme.title: Aneeshwar and Lizzie Go Wild S2 Ep16
programme.desc: Tamarin and Crowned Pigeon - Aneeshwar and Lizzie meet two amazing animals: this time it's the tamarin and crowned pigeon. Their wild connection is that they both have fancy "hairdos".

programme.title: Swashbuckle S8 Ep26
programme.desc: Gem's Magic Moments - Squawk takes us on a journey to find Gem's top Swashbuckle moments.

programme.title: Hey Duggee S4 Ep30
programme.desc: The Cinema Badge - Before the Squirrels attend the cinema for the first time, Duggee teaches them that there are rules they need to follow.

programme.title: Hey Duggee S4 Ep29
programme.desc: The Difficult Badge - As the Squirrels appreciate Norrie's new bike, they discover that she doesn't know how to ride it, she finds it too difficult.

programme.title: Hey Duggee S4 Ep28
programme.desc: The News Badge - After learning that Duggee is making his yearly batch of blueberry jam, a tradition passed on from his great-aunt, the Squirrels decide to spread the news.
